<div id="about">

<p>The National Science Foundation-funded Global Names project (Division of Biological Infrastructure, <%= link_to "#1062441", "http://www.nsf.gov/awardsearch/showAward.do?AwardNumber=1062441", :target => "_blank" %>) is a component of the <%= link_to "Global Names
Architecture", "http://www.globalnames.org" %> - conceived to provide an open and global names-based
infrastructure to index, organize and manage biodiversity data.</p>

<p>PostBox, in this initial version, is intended to provide an upload and preview facility for taxonomic checklists in Darwin Core Archive format. Future versions may include upload of spreadsheets with conversion into Darwin Core Archive, validation and cross-linking functions.</p>

